title: Dubai Bling
overview: Dubai Bling takes you behind the velvet rope to experience the glitz and glamour of life for the rich and famous in Dubai. Set against the backdrop of luxury cars, runway-fresh fashion, exotic resorts and exclusive access to the city's most popular restaurants and late-night hotspots, we follow the cast in their daily lives. It's not long before the competition between friends heats up and secrets are revealed, causing problems, sassy clapbacks and a whole lot of drama.Â
